-- Yemen Kidnappers Release Batis Cement Swedish Engineer, Yemen Post Reports
-- B y   M o h a m m e d   H a t e m
-- 2010-10-29T07:28:16Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-29/yemen-kidnappers-release-batis-cement-swedish-engineer-yemen-post-reports.html
A Swedish engineer working for Batis
Cement was freed a few hours after being kidnapped yesterday in
southern Yemen, the Yemen Post reported. The Swede was held by
tribesman who demanded authorities release a relative who was
jailed on a murder charge.  To contact the reporter on this story:
